---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About Jennifer Chong | Corporate Governance Expert Singapore"
  description="PhD in Corporate Governance. 8+ years of board research and consulting. Singapore's specialist in SGX compliance, board effectiveness and gender diversity."
>

<!-- ===== PAGE HERO ===== -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label" style="color:var(--gold-light);">About Jennifer</span>
    <h1>Jennifer Chong</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Corporate Governance Expert &amp; Female Director Recruitment Specialist<br>PhD in Board Effectiveness &nbsp;·&nbsp; 8+ Years Board Consulting Experience</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== -->
<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-layout">

      <!-- SIDEBAR -->
      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="about-profile-card">
          <div class="profile-img-placeholder">👩‍💼</div>
          <div class="about-profile-info">
            <h3>Jennifer Chong</h3>
            <p class="about-profile-title">PhD · Corporate Governance Consultant</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-stat-list">
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="lbl">Qualification</span>
            <span class="val">PhD (Curtin, 2023)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="lbl">Specialisation</span>
            <span class="val">Board Governance</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="lbl">Experience</span>
            <span class="val">8+ Years</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="lbl">Publications</span>
            <span class="val">3 (+ forthcoming)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="lbl">Current Role</span>
            <span class="val">Lecturer, ERC Institute</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="lbl">Location</span>
            <span class="val">Singapore</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Book Free Assessment</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline-navy" style="width:100%; justify-content:center;">View Services</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- MAIN -->
      <div>
        <div class="content-block">
          <span class="section-label">Overview</span>
          <h2>Who I Am</h2>
          <p>I'm a corporate governance expert helping Singapore's boards strengthen effectiveness, reach compliance targets, and build diverse leadership. My work combines academic research rigour with practical consulting experience, bridging the gap between governance theory and business reality.</p>
          <p>With a PhD in Corporate Governance and over 8 years of research focused on board effectiveness and gender diversity, I understand both the <em>why</em> (research evidence) and the <em>how</em> (practical implementation). I've published research in leading academic journals while simultaneously working directly with Singapore's boards on real-world governance challenges.</p>
          <p>I believe effective governance isn't just about compliance — it's about boards that make better decisions, develop leadership pipelines, attract investment, and create sustainable value. My mission is to help boards move from "compliance checkbox" to "governance excellence."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <span class="section-label">Academic Credentials</span>
          <h2>Education &amp; Qualifications</h2>

          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; margin-bottom:2rem;">
            <div class="highlight-box">
              <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.375rem;">PhD in Corporate Governance</h4>
              <p style="margin-bottom:0.25rem; color:var(--text-secondary);">Curtin University, 2023</p>
              <p style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--text-light); margin:0;"><em>Thesis: "Board Capital and Firm Performance: The Role of Board Involvement in Strategic Decision-Making and Investments in Big Data Analytics"</em></p>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:1.25rem; background:var(--gray-50); border-radius:var(--radius); border:1px solid var(--gray-200);">
              <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Master of Philosophy (Accounting)</h4>
              <p style="margin:0; color:var(--text-secondary); font-size:0.9375rem;">Curtin University, 2019</p>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:1.25rem; background:var(--gray-50); border-radius:var(--radius); border:1px solid var(--gray-200);">
              <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.25rem;">Bachelor of Commerce (Accounting &amp; Finance)</h4>
              <p style="margin:0; color:var(--text-secondary); font-size:0.9375rem;">Curtin University, 2016</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Publications &amp; Recognition</h3>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; margin-bottom:2rem;">
            <div class="pub-card fade-up">
              <div class="pub-journal">Journal of General Management · Mar 12, 2024</div>
              <div class="pub-title"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1177/03063070231218312" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;">"Gender Diversity, Education Diversity, and Big Data Analytics Investments — A Test of Moderation"</a></div>
              <p class="pub-meta">Lead Author &nbsp;·&nbsp; DOI: 10.1177/03063070231218312</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pub-card fade-up">
              <div class="pub-journal">MATEC Web of Conferences · Apr 17, 2023</div>
              <div class="pub-title"><a href="https://www.matec-conferences.org/articles/matecconf/abs/2023/04/matecconf_cgchdrc2022_02005/matecconf_cgchdrc2022_02005.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;">"Board Capital and Firm Performance"</a></div>
              <p class="pub-meta">Lead Author</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pub-card fade-up">
              <div class="pub-journal">Gender in Management: An International Journal</div>
              <div class="pub-title">"Board Involvement in Strategic Decision-Making and Big Data Analytics Investments — The Moderating Role of Gender Diversity" <span class="pub-status">Forthcoming</span></div>
              <p class="pub-meta">Lead Author</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Awards &amp; Recognition</h3>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.75rem;">
            <div class="award-item fade-up">
              <span class="award-icon">🏆</span>
              <div>
                <h5>Best Presentation Award</h5>
                <p>Curtin Global Campus Higher Degree by Research Colloquium, 2022</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="award-item fade-up">
              <span class="award-icon">🥇</span>
              <div>
                <h5>Best Poster Award</h5>
                <p>3rd Swinburne Sarawak Postgraduate Research Conference, 2022</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="award-item fade-up">
              <span class="award-icon">🎙</span>
              <div>
                <h5>3MT Competition Finalist</h5>
                <p>Curtin Malaysia Three Minute Thesis (3MT) Competition, 2022</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <span class="section-label">Professional Roles</span>
          <h2>Current &amp; Recent Positions</h2>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1.25rem;">
            <div style="padding:1.5rem 1.875rem; background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); border:1px solid var(--gray-200); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);">
              <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0.625rem;">
                <h4 style="color:var(--navy);">Lecturer — Corporate Governance &amp; Strategic Finance</h4>
                <span class="tag tag-green">Current</span>
              </div>
              <p style="font-weight:600; color:var(--gold); font-size:0.875rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">ERC Institute Singapore &nbsp;·&nbsp; Feb 2025 – Present</p>
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">Teaching strategic management, corporate governance, and professional practice. Student satisfaction ratings: 4.57–4.90/5.0, consistently exceeding university mean.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:1.5rem 1.875rem; background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); border:1px solid var(--gray-200); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);">
              <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0.625rem;">
                <h4 style="color:var(--navy);">Founder &amp; Board Governance Consultant</h4>
                <span class="tag tag-green">Current</span>
              </div>
              <p style="font-weight:600; color:var(--gold); font-size:0.875rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Jennifer Chong Consulting &nbsp;·&nbsp; Feb 2025 – Present</p>
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">Leading corporate governance consulting practice working directly with Singapore's boards on compliance, effectiveness, and diversity challenges.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="padding:1.5rem 1.875rem; background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); border:1px solid var(--gray-200); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);">
              <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.375rem;">Visiting Lecturer</h4>
              <p style="font-weight:600; color:var(--gold); font-size:0.875rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Swansea University &nbsp;·&nbsp; University of Chichester &nbsp;·&nbsp; Deakin University</p>
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:0.9375rem;">International academic engagement on corporate governance and board diversity topics across multiple universities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <span class="section-label">My Approach</span>
          <h2>Three Core Principles</h2>
          <div class="principles-grid" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
            <div class="principle-card fade-up">
              <div class="principle-num">01</div>
              <h4>Evidence-Based</h4>
              <p>My recommendations are grounded in rigorous research, not opinions. Academic rigour meets business practicality — every insight backed by published evidence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="principle-card fade-up">
              <div class="principle-num">02</div>
              <h4>Practical Implementation</h4>
              <p>Consulting isn't valuable if it doesn't get implemented. I don't just advise — I provide hands-on support to ensure recommendations become reality.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="principle-card fade-up">
              <div class="principle-num">03</div>
              <h4>Singapore-Focused</h4>
              <p>I understand Singapore's unique regulatory environment, business culture, and professional networks. My expertise is specific, not generic.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <span class="section-label">Why Governance Matters</span>
          <h2>The Board Governance Imperative</h2>
          <p>Your board shapes your organisation's future. After 8+ years of research, the evidence is clear:</p>
          <div class="grid-2" style="gap:1.5rem; margin-top:1.25rem;">
            <div>
              <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.875rem;">Strong boards achieve:</h4>
              <ul class="check-list">
                <li>Better strategic decisions (diverse perspectives, healthy debate)</li>
                <li>More effective risk management (catching what others miss)</li>
                <li>Greater investor confidence and capital attraction</li>
                <li>Stronger talent retention and leadership pipelines</li>
                <li>Regulatory compliance and reputational protection</li>
                <li>Sustainable long-term value creation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 style="color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.875rem;">Weak governance leads to:</h4>
              <ul class="check-list x-list">
                <li>Poor strategic choices and missed opportunities</li>
                <li>Unidentified and unmanaged risks</li>
                <li>SGX regulatory problems and reputational damage</li>
                <li>Leadership crises without succession plans</li>
                <li>Investor scepticism and reduced access to capital</li>
                <li>Talent drain from leadership pipeline failures</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to Learn More?</h2>
    <p>Explore my services, research, or get in touch to discuss your board's specific needs.</p>
    <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content:center;">
      <a href="/services"  class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">View Consulting Services</a>
      <a href="/research"  class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">See Publications</a>
      <a href="/contact"   class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Contact Me</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
